{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first, the feeling of being completely abandoned-- that there wasn't any chance to be rescued by any country in the world, because there was no sign of that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were constantly told by Churchill that he would be coming, for instance, next time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the fall leaves would fall, they would also be coming there to save us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we finally lost completely any hope to be saved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was becoming tighter and tighter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were having less and less to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were getting more and more fearful all the time because having deported so many people, there weren't that many left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we always believed that they finally would come to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was absolutely no way to relax or to think that things could be better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't see any end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We couldn't see any end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could have no-- no idea that the Americans would ever come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all we knew is that there-- a few Americans went to Canada.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from-- from Canada, they came in, parachuting, to France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's another thing we did-- we used to pick them up, when they were falling down, and bring them to-- they were brought to, or rather-- given an address-- they were given an address.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that address was given-- was changed for another address when they got to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they went to the next stop, and then the next stop, until they went to the last person who was sending them back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, this was one of the things we knew was happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that wasn't helping us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, they would-- they-- there wasn't-- there wasn't any way to be saved, and to think that this would finally be over.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
